data.description: This corner lot home is a must-see! The beautiful spring flower garden in the front yard adds to the charming curb appeal. Featuring a new wood fence, new water heater, and new living room flooring, this home is move-in ready. You'll also enjoy clean carpets, stainless steel appliances, and central air. Take a peek inside to fully appreciate all that this wonderful home has to offer!
